name: Periodic Table - Wooden Blocks - U, Ni, V, Er, Se
description:
This is a set of 5 blocks.
These are hand made wooden blocks decorated with the periodic elements. Each block has been cut, sanded painted on one face white then screen printed with the chemical element.

Perfect for all the science enthusiasts out there.

The block measures: 10cm tall, 7cm wide and 4.5cm in depth.

Due to the fluid nature of the techniques used in creating them each block may vary slightly in grain and print from the one shown.

Shipping: 
UK: 2.00 
Everywhere else: £8.00
